{"tid":2478713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加建議世界盃應改為兩年一屆","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T09:23:40.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a298a372680ff8cad1d9e6299a07aef42f424ace","tid":2478713,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XCsjCVl8kk6WPrPN6FTtNo13uEg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2QJUCNNBNFXZAPH6EUCRSH5S4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXCsjCVl8kk6WPrPN6FTtNo13uEg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI2QJUCNNBNFXZAPH6EUCRSH5S4.jpg&h=918b3ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現職<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">國際足協全球足球發展總監</span></span></strong>的前阿仙奴領隊雲加建議，現時四年一度的世界盃應改為每兩年一屆，讓球員有更多機會趁着職業生涯高峯時期，贏得這項球壇最高榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n雲加早前接受傳媒訪問時說：「<strong><span class=\"red\">假如你看一看歷屆世界盃各隊的陣容，平均年齡大約是27、28歲。由於每四年才有一屆世界盃，他們再次參賽時，已經是32至33歲了，所以很少有球員可以贏得多過一次冠軍。正因如此，或許我們應該每兩年便舉行一屆世界盃。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n過往曾多次批評歐國聯的雲加認為，應該集中資源舉辦世界盃與歐國盃等「有意義」的賽事。「取消其他所有賽事吧，我們只應該舉辦有意義的比賽。」雲格續道。<br />\n<br />\n雲加又指，國際足協正研究如何壓縮各項大賽的外圍賽賽程，削減國際賽期，以減少對各地本土聯賽的影響。他說：「最理想的方案，是在一個月內完成所有外圍賽，例如說是10月，完成外圍賽後，你就可以全季專注為球會上陣。」雲加又指，無論最終的討論結果如何，球員的休季時間也要得到保障。「以現今球員的體能需求來看，讓球員擁有四周假期是非常重要的。」雲加補充說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球足球發展總監呢個朵又幾撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9205111db8f894ccd119e6c59a8526091ee4945d","tid":2478713,"uid":370705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:17:51.000Z","msg":"咁咪無左嗰種獨特性 就係四年一度先咁珍貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6166cac85178a583c10d6006e92ed5e144522f","tid":2478713,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"半年一屆啦"},{"pid":"703a32c3e358f5bec678427399555d9fd1553aac","tid":2478713,"uid":351466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:20:40.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cb95d9f776a20c8abb543311820827a2c71b2e","tid":2478713,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">雲加~! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p>"},{"pid":"23d91e4f1d127758bb697200799155f67837bc47","tid":2478713,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:21:57.000Z","msg":"問左歐洲足協既發展總監未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752305346bbde2edaa5504c6cdfafd387673b0d3","tid":2478713,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3cb95d9f776a20c8abb543311820827a2c71b2e","tid":2478713,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">雲加~! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"雲加雲雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}